        </ul>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">Not sure how to manage your Google profile? Check out our <a href="/services/digital-marketing-local-seo" class="text-primary hover:underline">Local SEO services</a> to learn how we can help.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- Section 2: Focus on Website Speed and Mobile-Friendliness -->
      <section class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-foreground flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary text-lg">2</span>
          Focus on Website Speed and Mobile-Friendliness
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">Google cares about one thing when it comes to your website: <strong>how easy it is for users to find what they need.</strong> If your website is slow, hard to navigate, or doesn’t work well on mobile, <strong>Google will rank you lower in search results.</strong></p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">Here’s how to improve your website today:</p>
        <ul class="grid gap-4 pl-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Make sure your site loads in under 3 seconds</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
