          Automate Your Review Requests
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">Getting more reviews is one of the fastest ways to improve your SEO. But manually asking every customer for a review? <strong>That’s a waste of time.</strong> Our <a href="/services/business-automations" class="text-primary hover:underline">Business Automation services</a> handle this for you.</p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">Here’s how it works: after a customer uses your service, they’ll automatically get a text or email asking them to leave a review. It’s simple, effective, and saves you hours of manual work.</p>
      </section>

